"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/9/34970?source=see_link\">",
"      Definition, pathogenesis, and etiology of polycystic ovary syndrome in adolescents",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?38/36/39495?source=see_link\">",
