"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/27/16826?source=see_link\">",
"      Metformin for treatment of the polycystic ovary syndrome",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?23/28/24007?source=see_link\">",
"      Pathogenesis and causes of hirsutism",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/37/35416?source=see_link\">",
